{"tid":1662250,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"耿爽: 我地鬼有要求NBA炒Morey?","createTime":"2019-10-18T15:40:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T16:50:53.000Z","uid":147785,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"57c3282d59d343db339875f7bf7db147e3125196","tid":1662250,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T15:40:45.000Z","msg":"During that same appearance, Silver revealed that the Chinese government told the NBA it wanted Morey fired.<br />\n<br />\n阿銀話中共政府要求NBA炒Morey<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Obviously, we made clear that we were being asked to fire him by the Chinese government, by the parties we dealt with, government and business,&rdquo; Silver said. &ldquo;We said, &lsquo;There&rsquo;s no chance that&rsquo;s happening. There&rsquo;s no chance we&rsquo;ll even discipline him.&rsquo;&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n澄清番 我地係被中共政府 同不同機構組織 要求炒Morey<br />\n但我地對此既回覆就係:「無可能！甚至唔會要求佢收聲！」<br />\n<br />\nBut Friday, Chinese Foreign Ministry spokesman Geng Shuang rebutted by saying, &ldquo;the Chinese government never posed this requirement.&rdquo; Geng said last week that the NBA &ldquo;knows better than anyone else&rdquo; how to go about repairing the relationship with the Chinese, though did not offer specifics.<br />\n<br />\n今日晚上 中國口交部發言人耿爽: 「我地鬼有咁要求過?」<br />\n「NBA比任何人都清楚知道要點先可以同中國修補關係 就算我地唔講出口」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://apnews.com/f721ead046f742dba80b7b5a9cff0876\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Ff721ead046f742dba80b7b5a9cff0876&d=hAhx4mZ6jCiP%2Fv5W8BSz9oHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=6505c751\" target=\"_blank\">https://apnews.com/f721ead046f742dba80b7b5a9cff0876</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hoopsrumors.com/2019/10/adam-silver-china-wanted-daryl-morey-fired.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hoopsrumors.com%2F2019%2F10%2Fadam-silver-china-wanted-daryl-morey-fired.html&d=hAhx4mZ6jCiP%2Fv5W8BSz9oHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=9d793b6b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hoopsrumors.com/2019/10/adam-silver-china-wanted-daryl-morey-fired.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你 如果你無咁做 銀仔會寧願放棄幾百億生意都要 無啦啦老作屈你?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全世界都知銀仔眼中只有錢 係無人估到佢今次居然企硬<br />\n<br />\n所以銀仔企硬幫Morey已經好難得 但成個twitter居然無人講<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好再錯過埋呢次好無? 你估撥火機會長期有?<br />\n<br />\n篇報導出咗無耐架咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3a871a83a6b2a8c0518bc8ef8feb2d21db875d9","tid":1662250,"uid":2419,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T15:41:32.000Z","msg":"睇錯耿鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e2624d8a3e5320ee9dc6719914f7b20a0f87df6","tid":1662250,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3a871a83a6b2a8c0518bc8ef8feb2d21db875d9","tid":1662250,"uid":2419,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T15:41:32.000Z","msg":"睇錯耿鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T15:41:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dac7d8e3f285298ec20604b1613ce34ce977d801","tid":1662250,"uid":1425,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f3a871a83a6b2a8c0518bc8ef8feb2d21db875d9","tid":1662250,"uid":2419,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T15:41:32.000Z","msg":"睇錯耿鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T15:42:18.000Z","msg":"睇錯恥夾"},{"pid":"9659328b18a3574144fad419bbdbda6e630d862b","tid":1662250,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T15:46:29.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"65f3a68039d595f1d9fb04833bdea2db46c90ff9","tid":1662250,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T15:47:12.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"8c395bbff8978f184fd1dc3c755e29028e28aba3","tid":1662250,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":